org.jamwiki.servlets

Class WikiPageInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jamwiki.servlets.WikiPageInfo

  • public class WikiPageInfo
extends Object
    The WikiPageInfo class provides an object containing common data used for generating wiki page display.

      • getVirtualWikiName

        public String getVirtualWikiName()
